   *bm2font-2.0*
   -------------

   - what is it?
     Bm2font: convert a bitmap to a TeX font

   - homepage
     - http://vega.rz.uni-duesseldorf.de/sowa/bm2font/bm2font/bm2font.html
	 
   - system
     - Windows95/98/2000/NT with msvcrt.dll
     - if msvcrt.dll is not in your Windows/System folder, get it
       from http://www.simtel.net/simtel.net/win95/dll
       or by installing Internet Explorer 4.0 or higher

   - notes
     - see also bm2font.htm

   - package availability
     - in: http://download.sourceforge.net/gnuwin32/
     - as: bm2font-2.0-bin.zip

   - documentation
     - bm2font-2.0-doc.zip
   
   - compilation:
     - preliminaries
       - get the source package
         - bm2font-2.0-src.zip
      - configure
        - works without changes
      - make
        - works without changes with Mingw32 (http://www.mingw.org)
      - make install
        - works without changes
